Helicopter Crash in Mexico City Kills 2, Injures State Minister

-- B y   N a c h a   C a t t a n
-- 
2011-10-21T17:04:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/helicopter-crash-in-mexico-city-kills-2-injures-state-minister.html
A helicopter crashed in the Coyoacan
area of  Mexico  City, killing two people and injuring Fernando
Alberto Garcia, the metropolitan development minister of the
state of Mexico, who was aboard the aircraft, Mexico City
attorney general Miguel Angel Mancera told Milenio TV.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nacha Cattan in Mexico City at 
 ncattan@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Joshua Goodman  at 
 jgoodman19@bloomberg.net . 